column2: SELECT   m.cent_gal_ID AS id,    m.ra AS ra,    m.dec AS dec,   o.deVRad_r AS Re,   o.nprof_r AS nprof,   p.profMean as prof_mean into mydb.MyTable from MyDB.CAM_CATALOGUE AS m   CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n   JOIN photoObjAll AS o ON n.objid=o.objid   JOIN photoProfile AS p on n.objid=p.objid
